{"type": "article", "id": 20421, "title": "可替换接口的水龙头", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-08T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104624K82kWtDCQOnYgUdu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款水龙头的出水口是一个橡胶做的黑色的球，它上面的金属片是可以打开的。打开后将橡胶球拉出，它就可以替换了。一旦发现水质不好，就可以重新换一个出水口。设计者希望用它来帮助流出的自来水保持纯净，而它新颖的造型本身也很有吸引力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104622bZh4fKsMgEJGXpS0.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"643\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104623JZyXqIYM3sOLx6mR.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"783\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104623rDYAnO9u1e5zqxU0.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"592\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n"}